translation.Message_0_Page_0: Thank you for being a great soldier. Here's your fatigues, now go out there and make this <color=blue>Navy</color> proud!
translation.Message_0_Page_1: Oh, by the way, we were planning on launching a few operations regarding the <color=red>Irish Freedom Republic</color>. Go talk to <color=legendary>Commander Keith</color> in the briefing room.
